title: bepositive
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Salad bar, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. All veg except for fish. Self-service buffet (mostly vegetarian) eatery and health food shop. Offers salad bar, soups, quiches, sandwiches, desserts, fruit and vegetable juices, cold and hot drinks.
